::Hot Rod::

He stared at Unicron. Unicron still hadn't acknowlaged his being there.
Thought he would be more worryed about the bot that blew up his body
before. Hot Rod glanced back at CliffJumper and BeachComber.
"It's good to see you guys." 
He looked back to Unicron.
"Come on, lets finish this."

::DrillBit::

He shot two optic blasts at Unitron, and then opened gattaling gun fire.
"DIE!!!!!!"

::Epyon::

He made sure the shot was perfect. It was. He launched a grenade right
at Rampage's head.

::Dollon::

He also continued to fire on Unitron. He woundered why the bot hadn't
fought back yet.

::Demolition::

Hed just looked at WolfGang. This bot had some seroius hits to the head
or something.

::KitKat2::

She walked from the bridge, she hadn' found anything. She knew she was
in the Alliance base, but that was all. She had to get back to the Pack.
